WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.470 --> 00:00:03.750
Bu mashqda men sizga uni 
qanday moslashtirishni aniq aytmayman.

00:00:03.750 --> 00:00:06.300
Katerina xohlaganidek, qo‘lingizdan 
biroz qo‘yib yuboraman.

00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:09.700
Bu sizga muammo nima ekanligini
tushunish va salohiyatli 

00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:11.750
yechim nimaligini tushunishingizga imkon beradi.

00:00:11.750 --> 00:00:15.140
Men sizni kodni tekshirib ko‘rishingizni va 
mana bu savollarga javob berishingizni xohlardim.

00:00:15.140 --> 00:00:18.260
Birinchisi, PhraseActivity ning nimasi noto‘g‘ri va 

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:19.700
nima uchun bu sodir bo‘lyapti deb o‘ylaysiz?

00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:21.660
Davom eting va javobingizni mana bu yerga yozing.

00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:25.920
Ikkinchisi, bu muammoni to‘g‘irlashimiz uchun 
kodni qanday qilib o‘zgartira olishimizni tasvirlang, shunda 

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:30.050
bizning ilovamiz sonlar sahifasi 
mana bunga va iboralar sahifasi

00:00:30.050 --> 00:00:31.720
mana bunga o‘xshab qoladi.

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.990
Bu yerga asl kodni yozishni keragi yo‘q.

00:00:33.990 --> 00:00:38.010
Shunchaki yondashuvingizni aniq detallar 
bilan ifodalang shunda 

00:00:38.010 --> 00:00:42.180
keyingi bosqichda siz o‘sha fikrlarni 
kodga osongina o‘gira olasiz.

00:00:42.180 --> 00:00:45.120
Agar sizga ba’zi ko‘rsatmalar kerak bo‘lsa, 
topshiriq pastidagi qaydlarni tekshirib ko‘ring.

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:48.270
Hozircha, bo‘sh joy qoldirish va ilovaning 
vizual ko‘rinishi haqida qayg‘urmang.

00:00:48.270 --> 00:00:49.590
Biz bu haqida keyingi bosqichlarda ish bajaramiz.

